{"tid":2295521,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"港共有Apple Google 武肺 API唔用，走去整個垃圾「安心出行」app 有乜居心？","createTime":"2020-11-22T00:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T01:05:39.000Z","uid":42884,"like":160,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5942ef38eb90dec0d779bd90793496a49e99f0f4","tid":2295521,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:35:37.000Z","msg":"全世界政府都用緊Apple Google 出嗰個COVID-19 exposure notification<br />\n一來data 唔會upload 上server，<br />\n二來唔洗track人嘅location<br />\n三來background 運作唔洗人主動scan QR code<br />\n而且只係用藍芽exchange 停留十分鐘二米距離嘅手機<br />\n設計上完全考慮私隱問題<br />\niOS 同Android 可以一齊運作<br />\n有興趣就睇下Apple Google 個介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/covid19/exposurenotifications/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fcovid19%2Fexposurenotifications%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5rxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=58dbb0fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/covid19/exposurenotifications/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共個垃圾創科局就走去整個垃圾「安心出行」嘅垃圾App<br />\n香港有呢班垃圾搞創科真係勁落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟本就全心要track人location <br />\n初初自願後來強制<br />\n仲要白癡到要人去一個地方scan QR code"},{"pid":"fa7cd66c461bdcbae0d0a37726a89623acbae4b1","tid":2295521,"uid":4285,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:40:13.000Z","msg":"唔寫隻apps 點搵錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb02b1ad0570b372ea5aa383796cd599ac3914e","tid":2295521,"uid":2581,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:57:02.000Z","msg":"佢哋真係為香港市民服務就一早用咗呢個API，<br />\n兩間科技巨頭會諗唔贏你一個香港政府外判cap水公司？<br />\n<br />\n呢個安心出行個目的都幾明顯，可惜眼高手低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b60e6219bb4de121b946b272ed5e84f4410cf5","tid":2295521,"uid":241072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:10:53.000Z","